description:
A member of Xcution. She`s coming from abroad, but it`s unknown where she actually comes from.
Her Fullbring is called "Dirty Boots". As the name implicates it has something to do with the state of cleanlyness of her boots. That is, the more dirty they become during the fight - be it with mud, ash or blood - the stronger Jacky will be.
name: Jacky Tristan
